Hy nh rng, khng phi l ni dung ca bn. N thm ch khng phi l ni dung ca SoundCloud. Tt c m thanh, vn bn, hnh nh, nhn xt v d liu hoc thng tin khc c lin kt vi ti khon ngi dng trn nn tng SoundCloud ("Ni dung ngi dng") thuc quyn s hu ca ngi dng SoundCloud to hoc ti ln n ("Ngi ti ln") v bn phi tn trng quyn ca h mi lc. Vic s dng sai Ni dung ca Ngi dng c th cu thnh vi phm bn quyn v dn n vic Ngi ti ln hoc ch s hu bn quyn khc s thc hin hnh ng chng li bn.
